---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
<section class="bg-[#07001C] pt-32 pb-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
      <span class="bg-[#110833] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.3)] text-[#7C3AED] text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Creation de site</span>
      <h1 class="font-syne font-extrabold text-[#F1F0F7] mt-4 mb-6" style="font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);line-height:1.1;">Creation de site web pour entreprises reunionnaises</h1>
      <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-lg leading-relaxed">Sites vitrines, boutiques en ligne, applications metier — rapides, securises et bien references sur Google La Reunion.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-8 flex-wrap">
        <a href="tel:+262692311191" class="bg-[#7C3AED] hover:bg-[#6D28D9] text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all">Devis gratuit</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.4)] text-[#F1F0F7] hover:border-[#7C3AED] font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all">Nous contacter</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-[#0D0028] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.15)] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-syne font-bold text-[#F1F0F7] mb-3">Site vitrine</h3>
        <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm mb-3">Presentation de votre activite, equipe, services et coordonnees. Design professionnel, optimise mobile, heberge et maintenu.</p>
        <div class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold">A partir de 990 EUR</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#0D0028] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.15)] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-syne font-bold text-[#F1F0F7] mb-3">Site e-commerce</h3>
        <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm mb-3">Boutique en ligne avec paiement securise, gestion des stocks, livraison. Adaptee aux TPE/PME reunionnaises.</p>
        <div class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold">A partir de 2 490 EUR</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#0D0028] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.15)] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-syne font-bold text-[#F1F0F7] mb-3">Application metier</h3>
        <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm mb-3">Portail client, intranet, outil de gestion sur-mesure. Integrable avec Dolibarr ERP et vos outils existants.</p>
        <div class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold">Sur devis</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#0A0022] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.2)] rounded-2xl p-8 mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-syne font-bold text-[#F1F0F7] text-2xl mb-6">Inclus dans chaque projet</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold">&#10003;</span><span class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm">Design sur-mesure adapte a votre identite visuelle</span></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold">&#10003;</span><span class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm">Optimisation SEO (balises, vitesse, schema.org)</span></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold">&#10003;</span><span class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm">HTTPS et certificat SSL inclus</span></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold">&#10003;</span><span class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm">Compatible mobile et tablette</span></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold">&#10003;</span><span class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm">Hebergement sur serveur en France</span></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#7C3AED] font-bold">&#10003;</span><span class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm">Formation a l&#39;administration du site</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#0D0028] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.2)] rounded-xl p-6 max-w-xl">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Votre projet en tete ?</h3>
      <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm mb-4">Devis gratuit sous 48h — on etudie votre besoin sans engagement.</p>
      <a href="tel:+262692311191" class="bg-[#7C3AED] hover:bg-[#6D28D9] text-white text-sm font-medium px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-all inline-block">0692 31 11 91</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
